  "detailed_description": "Cyberpunch is a post apocalyptic beat em up game. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503350/extras/ffbae69f2aa78e1ae4c43052a87372d3.avif?t=1687233332\" width=680 height=432 /></span><br><br>The fast-paced action is peppered with a variety of unique enemies with speeds, health and attacks of each enemy found at all levels generated by procedure or randomly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503350/extras/2c4c66a565543153f61605801daf86d3.avif?t=1687233332\" width=680 height=432 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503350/extras/fc8dd113529d102302a9315d965dfe62.avif?t=1687233332\" width=600 height=272 /></span><br><br>Controller Support<br>This game has Full Controller Support.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503350/extras/bee0579665e29e7a1e9b2088fc6d84e6.avif?t=1687233332\" width=680 height=432 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1503350/extras/12e59182780d02a9957260ea01f46bef.avif?t=1687233332\" width=600 height=170 /></span>",
